Title: [GPS Manager][GPS Insights][Stop Time Analysis Report]Validate Stop Duration Logic
Description: Test case to verify stop duration filtering logic in Stop Time Analysis Report results
Precondition: 1. Data loaded; 2. Report results are visible; 3. Stop duration data contains expected values
Steps: 1. Review the loaded report data for stop duration values; 2. Locate the stop duration column in the results; 3. Verify each row shows stop duration values; 4. Check that durations under 5 minutes are displayed as stops; 5. Confirm durations more than 5 minutes show as parked; 6. Validate the 5-minute threshold logic; 7. Verify all stop entries exceed the input duration requirement
Expected Result: 1. Loaded report data displays stop duration values clearly; 2. Stop duration column is visible and contains data; 3. Each row shows appropriate stop duration values; 4. Durations under 5 minutes are correctly displayed as stops; 5. Durations more than 5 minutes are correctly shown as parked; 6. 5-minute threshold logic is working correctly; 7. All stop entries exceed the input duration requirement as expected
